{"tid":2353147,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《星島》指北京在港建「文化央企」　中聯辦出手　統一聯合出版等機構推動人心回歸","createTime":"2021-01-04T13:24:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T08:39:53.000Z","uid":271829,"like":5,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"f29e0fd48f6077598af899a30539e25105b06bbc","tid":2353147,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:24:41.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n建制報章《星島日報》今日報道，北京政府將在香港組建「文化央企」，以提升中央在港的「軟實力」，相關「文化央企」將由中聯辦秘書長文宏武參與籌建，統一管轄聯合出版集團、《紫荊》雜誌社、銀都機構及中華文化城等中資機構，由出版、印刷、新聞、新媒體、影視、文藝演出都包辦，藉此「推動人心回歸」，預料今年上半年開張。<br />\n<br />\n《星島日報》今日引述消息稱，今年52歲、形同中聯辦「大管家」的秘書長文宏武參與籌建「文化央企」，指文宏武本身是出版家，熟悉文化運營，早於2008年來港擔任聯合出版（集團）有限公司董事長兼總裁，2018年起任中聯辦秘書長。<br />\n該報指，聯合出版（集團）是「文化央企」的龍頭，旗下包括三聯書店、中華書局和商務印書館（三中商）、萬里機構、新雅文化事業公司等多家出版機構，出版圖書量約佔香港每年中文圖書出版量五分一。近年經常攻擊、抹黑民主派的網媒「橙新聞」，亦屬聯合出版旗下媒體。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0uVAcctaHMye-x51sMFRyCDyzeg=/1600x1200/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YEWOKROKNT2LWHM74NCBHCALOQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0uVAcctaHMye-x51sMFRyCDyzeg%3D%2F1600x1200%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYEWOKROKNT2LWHM74NCBHCALOQ.jpg&h=276c092a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聯合出版（集團）是「文化央企」的龍頭，旗下包括三聯書店、中華書局（圖）和商務印書館（三中商）、萬里機構、新雅文化事業公司等多家出版機構，出版圖書量約佔香港每年中文圖書出版量五分一。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，港台節目《鏗鏘集》2018年5月曾當面查詢中聯辦宣傳文體部副部長李海堂，中聯辦是否聯合出版的大股東和大老闆？惟李海堂當時只回應說：「你說的情況我不清楚」，中聯辦副主任陳東更說：「我們沒有分管這方面的事」，又說自己「不是很了解」有關事情。<br />\n本身為聯合出版出任第一任董事長兼總裁的李祖澤，則在節目中確認聯合出版集團屬國有資產，並受中聯辦管理。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210104/OOB3FVCNKJBVLEORMJTNS6KD2U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210104%2FOOB3FVCNKJBVLEORMJTNS6KD2U%2F&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuOYgDU6S0x1vJ5b5MQMl6fZo%3D&h=8e82d887\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210104%2FOOB3FVCNKJBVLEORMJTNS6KD2U%2F&h=2c6e6906\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210104/OOB3FVCNKJBVLEORMJTNS6KD2U/</a>"},{"pid":"8d2d124b0a4e25356469e501da6786d6ab775a71","tid":2353147,"uid":113929,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:31:17.000Z","msg":"開始清洗書籍<br />\n商務多咗好多藍營既書<br />\n圖書館好多敏感少少既書都無咗"},{"pid":"df5ff73f835517c27443268c7f6e47900142a1ac","tid":2353147,"uid":214502,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:33:38.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />飯到冇得食 樓都買唔撚到"},{"pid":"c58b5af0e5791aae55c2ca7c27f19cc4ba75dbf2","tid":2353147,"uid":36178,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:36:41.000Z","msg":"等睇中聯辦又搞鑊勁嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cc7f8e6a6b7808707277835b5a5d2302355f700","tid":2353147,"uid":2054,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:39:23.000Z","msg":"星島幾時執？<br />\n媒體收編曬份垃圾無科水價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b155bf9219a9a31f57e6ba4955148594fbb5604","tid":2353147,"uid":80724,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:40:32.000Z","msg":"2021年重諗住人心回歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b504cd95052a6343d888d6857c6c365c23c28638","tid":2353147,"uid":23786,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:43:11.000Z","msg":"食緊和牛、日本士多啤梨，算唔算犯國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dba0b5f12e0947bbab951a8adaf35ad97a72c95d","tid":2353147,"uid":51583,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:45:09.000Z","msg":"ON9先會覺得呢D方法仲有用"},{"pid":"5027dc9934e6321018cf38f06bbf1373d9c06d47","tid":2353147,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:46:42.000Z","msg":"不如個個月派錢好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b578f298e884762cfe6e1b54a0222fe2eef5eaf7","tid":2353147,"uid":118520,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dba0b5f12e0947bbab951a8adaf35ad97a72c95d","tid":2353147,"uid":51583,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:45:09.000Z","msg":"ON9先會覺得呢D方法仲有用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T13:48:48.000Z","msg":"21 世紀仲睇書？"},{"pid":"4a6c737f48507567370750fca0d8e0181458ba6f","tid":2353147,"uid":183509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T17:22:43.000Z","msg":"圖書館都係經三中商入書ga<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40132ece30ee7b71da3c59baa53f8a19f1945e28","tid":2353147,"uid":98477,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T17:51:16.000Z","msg":"今時唔同往日<br />\n<br />\n願意俾錢買圖書睇嘅人，學識都有返咁上下，寧願上網買英文書/去其他地方買台版書，都唔會去睇三中商最近三幾年出版嗰啲垃圾<br />\n<br />\n三中商優勢在於多舖，同埋願意翻印一啲無咁大路嘅文化掌故類舊書（例如三中商再版返上世紀三十年代嘅《香港便覽》，又出返五十年代講塘西掌故嘅小報專欄集《塘西花月痕》）。但除咗掌故撚，睇新書嘅人都唔會去幫襯三中商<br />\n<br />\n又，最近幾年三中商大量出版外國社科類書嘅中譯本，但好多都係簡轉繁就算，入面嘅用詞同句子好多都係硬譯出嚟，真係唔適合香港人睇。"},{"pid":"c43f10c49b1c3d95e13e319e248c68de689e3fd5","tid":2353147,"uid":76603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T17:53:57.000Z","msg":"香港人都移民啦 我肉身回歸大英祖國先"},{"pid":"e29e3cccac4887a55eb1bb717ed5823908879330","tid":2353147,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T17:55:18.000Z","msg":"人參回歸，係香港種？"},{"pid":"388a12af34d0b05b49f4e262b1a6dbf8d23849c3","tid":2353147,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T17:56:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0uVAcctaHMye-x51sMFRyCDyzeg%3D%2F1600x1200%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYEWOKROKNT2LWHM74NCBHCALOQ.jpg&amp;h=276c092a&amp;s=540\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n開頭仲有